com.t2.biofeedback
Class BioFeedbackServiceManagerReceiver

java.lang.Object
  BroadcastReceiver
      com.t2.biofeedback.BioFeedbackServiceManagerReceiver

public class BioFeedbackServiceManagerReceiver
extends BroadcastReceiver

Receiver of broadcast intent messages from 3 different sources: 1. BTServiceManager (Activity) - Startup and shutdown 2. Android BluetoothAdapter - Bluetooth hardware adapter turned on/off 3. AndroidSpineServer (Activity) - Messages to send to sensor devices (i.e "Discover")

Author:
scott.coleman
